<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="register-v">register <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'redʒɪstə(r)/    美 /'redʒɪstər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>注册；登记：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>How many students have <strong>registered for</strong> English classes? 
有多少学生登记选修英语课了？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>All visitors should <strong>register with</strong> the British Embassy. 
所有游客都必须到英国大使馆登记。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>registration /ˌredʒɪ'streɪʃn/ n <br />
1. <strong>登记；注册；挂号</strong>  </p>
<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>According to the law, all foreigners have to register <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ the local police within two weeks of arrival.  （2013 湖北改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. with  </p></div>